{"tid":432880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"這是一個黃金時代","createTime":"2017-10-12T02:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T02:13:43.000Z","uid":33095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf83e0025c0b8fdb5930862f1a575246645f818","tid":432880,"uid":33095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"當足球有美欺丙朗<br />\n網球有費達拿拿度<br />\n羽毛球有林丹李宗偉<br />\n分別係幾項運動統治左起碼十年<br />\n甚至被人稱為球壇史上最強 沒有之一<br />\n彼此都係最強對手惺惺相惜<br />\n當然你可以話會有長江後浪推前浪<br />\n但試問我又點會捨得佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/101305_e28b07f364e93adfad441872e1f4506f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F101305_e28b07f364e93adfad441872e1f4506f.jpg&h=d8936fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/101308_33303270f4013d321d489b21253491d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F101308_33303270f4013d321d489b21253491d8.jpg&h=f48a356e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/101308_77e351bd9c52d523716b596599ea16ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F101308_77e351bd9c52d523716b596599ea16ae.jpg&h=8c450fe2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}